snippet.title: KVLT - Wolfshöhle's Barracks Gameplay (@ZlimBratSki's Indie FPS Summer Showcase)
snippet.description:
FELLOW KVLTISTS

We wanted to share with you some progress on KVLT's development, this is gameplay captured from the second level of the game: Wolfshöhle.

In this level Lazar will infiltrate one of Fenrir's Underground bases and have to fight his way through barracks, facilities, a giant foundry and even more ancient Eldritch secrets!

JOIN THE KVLT: https://bit.ly/jointhekvlt
Play demo and wishlist at: https://bit.ly/playkvlt

Originally premiered at  Zlimbratski's Indie FPS Summer 2024 Showcase: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8tG-jv3BGYA
